external_knowledge:
Hydropower and marine technologies are renewable energy sources that can significantly reduce carbon emissions; 
Carbon reduction is a key metric in evaluating a project's environmental impact, as it directly relates to the reduction of greenhouse gases;
Energy savings in kWh is a common metric for measuring the efficiency of renewable energy projects;
Feedback types (positive, negative, neutral) provide insight into community perceptions of the projects.

sql:
SELECT stakeholder_name
FROM project_stakeholders
WHERE role = 'Community Leader';

SELECT community_name
FROM communities
WHERE energy_consumption = (SELECT MAX(energy_consumption) FROM communities);

